Security
All security decisions documented in docs/planning/SECURITY_DECISIONS.md.
Key points:
	∙	BLE uses LESC passkey pairing (not Just Works)
	∙	WiFi credentials double-encrypted (BLE link + AES-128-GCM)
	∙	Secrets stored in /etc/bitos/secrets (root-owned, mode 600)
	∙	Default PIN is 0000 — change via Settings → PIN after first boot

